2011 – Laboratório Químico Farmacêutico Bergamo Ltda.[39]
2012 – Micromet, Inc.[40]
2012 – Mustafa Nevzat İlaç[41][42]
2012 – KAI Pharmaceuticals[43]
2012 – deCODE genetics
2013 – Onyx Pharmaceuticals Inc.[44]
2015 – Dezima Pharma[23]
2015 – Catherex[45]


